attachments.title: New funding for Jupyter
attachments.text: We are pleased to announce that the Jupyter/IPython project has received $6M in funding from three organisations: The Leona M. and Harry B. Helmsley Charitable Trust The Gordon and Betty Moore Foundation The Alfred P. Sloan Foundation The grant,...
